STATE of North Carolina
v.
Anthony E. WILKINS. No. 169P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 10, 2005. Anthony E. Wilkins, Pro Se. Joan M. Cunningham, Assistant Attorney General, Mitchell D. Norton, District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 21st day of March 2005 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Beaufort County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 4th day of May 2005."
